query:
SELECT 
  i.id,
  p.sku,
  p.description,
  i.quantity,
  i.reservedQuantity,
  wl.code as locationCode,
  wz.code as zoneCode
FROM inventory i
JOIN products p ON p.id = i.productId
JOIN warehouseLocations wl ON wl.id = i.locationId
JOIN warehouseZones wz ON wz.id = wl.zoneId
WHERE wz.code = 'EXP'
AND p.sku IN ('4014609', '443060', '834207')
ORDER BY p.sku;
